<p>Throw them in jail where, if there&#39;s any such thing as justice, they&#39;ll get broom-raped like Linda Blair on a daily basis.</p>
<p class="posted">Posted by: Queer Supremacist | Feb 8, 2015 11:34:00 PM</p><br /></span></li>


